      "score": 36,
      "comments": 9,
      "author": "hoistbypetard",
      "published": "2026-06-16T12:58:11Z",
      "bullets": [
        "Threat actors bypass email security by delivering malicious PDF, LNK, or ZIP payloads directly through LinkedIn direct messaging channels.",
        "Spear-phishing campaigns often deploy the \"More_eggs\" backdoor or Trojanized coding challenges to compromise developer and security analyst endpoints.",
        "Defense requires monitoring endpoint process spawns like `mshta.exe` or `powershell.exe` originating from web browsers or untrusted downloaded archives."
      ]
